➜从前从黔。
http://www.sohu.com/a/412346748_428120	14267
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200810/9bf3f9aa3bdf4e0ca708bc149b0af496.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">旅行，有时只为获取</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">那瞬间的疏离和巨大的与世隔离。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">在黔贵一隅，你可以，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">尽情享受这般决然的滋味。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">古寨清江藏旧事，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这趟旅行，风情万种。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200810/dd93cfb7e70a4f7cbd5e59e9f807c210.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这是一条时光隧道，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">历史沉淀和渊源无与伦比。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200810/5ab41e6ad0eb476e94bbad4e8e0379c8.png" max-width="600" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
<div class="lookall-shadow"></div>
<section class="lookall">
<a href="javascript:;" class="show-all" id="showMore">
<em>展开全文</em>
</a>
</section>
</div>
<div class="hidden-content control-hide">
<p class="ql-align-center">这里，隐居着一群侠客，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">发髻、火铳，浊酒，笙笛。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200810/176f338ce1a84fb9b941054daa820a0e.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>这一次，你想以怎样方式，</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>与他们重逢。</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>花桥、戏台，</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>鼓楼，吊脚。</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">他们历世事沧桑，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">如今却低沉不语。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200810/ac80a0617dcd4048971f6e8b1bb2ae1c.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">如果你爱，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">请与我们沉入这烟火处，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">一起凝视。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这一次，我们从<strong>西江千户苗寨</strong>说起。</p>
<p>凯里的东南，从雷山路口折向东北，是凯里周围规模最大的苗寨。这里的房屋大多是木吊脚楼，用枫木搭成，依山势向两边展开。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200810/8820dba816024270a48c2e85018bde07.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">选一个夜晚，一家家的灯火点上，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">伴随着自己半醉半醒的状态，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">再看西江苗寨万家灯火，宛如星空之城。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>裙摆红艳，珮环作响，</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>笙声不息，灯火不灭。</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200810/676ed3b8e4b64ba0b9d46e4662532118.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p><strong>肇兴侗寨</strong>，梯田环绕着寨子，河流穿寨而过，鼓楼相望花桥相连，侗家人在晨雾里劳作于田埂之上，黄昏时坐在花桥聊天乘凉。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200810/ee06456c0ba945828b4644cc0fc65787.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">野性和浪漫，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">是这个寨子最真实的面孔。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">百日千锤成侗衣，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">侗寨家家户户门前及沿河的护栏上都挂满了侗布，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">你会听见远处不时传来捶打的声音。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200810/d49b48b61506425399a4bf13ba9f0698.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200810/89abeafdb6d243f6b3c76bc90c506078.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">一曲笙歌奏毕，三声铁铳响起，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">火枪对天鸣放，打开寨门迎宾入内，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这里藏着一群火枪手，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">神秘岜沙。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200810/6543a92a5f644a7a847384c3998f6a22.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">“生也一棵树，死也一棵树”，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">在岜沙，一棵树就是一个灵魂。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200810/053b3f50944e4c58a4102a65a88fbab9.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">锋利的镰刀从头顶划过</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">像割倒一片片成熟的庄稼</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">堆起苗寨男人们独有的粮仓</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200810/bc5532acf31b415a877fd76b654ba6eb.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">而腰刀火枪自治的铜扣青布衣</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">是岜沙悄悄藏在岁月之外的青翠</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">从中原的战场一路撤走 隐在这青山绿水间</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200810/15fbd212bb1546249716a5c1c08a1c1e.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>全文完，感谢阅读。</strong></p>
